{"id": "1670515269", "isEnabled": true, "objectTypeId": "0-3", "flowType": "WORKFLOW", "revisionId": "20", "name": "Bot Hook | Inspection", "description": "Sends SMS and email updates about the Site Survey phase to customers in Colorado managed by a specific project manager, then triggers a webhook and notifies an internal user.", "uuid": "Bot Hook | Inspection-1670515269", "createdAt": "2025-07-10T13:08:00.792Z", "updatedAt": "2026-04-08T21:41:05.767Z", "startActionId": "2", "nextAvailableActionId": "8", "actions": [{"actionId": "1", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "3"}, "fields": {"property_name": "project_status", "value": {"staticValue": "This is a {{ enrolled_object.project_type }} project worth a contract value of {{ enrolled_object.amount }}. The project stage is {{ enrolled_object.dealstage }}.\n\nThe sales consultant is {{ enrolled_object.hubspot_owner_id }}. \n\nThe project manager is {{ enrolled_object.project_manager }}. \n\nThis project is based out of our {{ enrolled_object.pb_location }} office. \n\nThe address for this job is {{ enrolled_object.address_line_1 }}, {{ enrolled_object.city }}, {{ enrolled_object.state }} {{ enrolled_object.postal_code }}.\n\nThe Authority Having Jurisdiction (AHJ) is {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153828501.record_name }}. They take {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153828501.permit_turnaround_average }} days to approve permits. \n\nThe utility company for this address is {{ enrolled_object.utility_company }}\n\nThe site survey status is {{ enrolled_object.site_survey_status }}.\n\nThe design approval status is{{ enrolled_object.layout_status }}.\n\nThe design & engineering status is {{ enrolled_object.design_status }}. \n\nThe permit status is {{ enrolled_object.permitting_status }}. The permit submission date is: {{ enrolled_object.permit_submit_date }}. The permit issued date is {{ enrolled_object.permit_completion_date }}. \n\nThe interconnection application status with the utility company is {{ enrolled_object.interconnection_status }}.\n\nThe construction status is {{ enrolled_object.install_status }}. \n\nThe inspection status is {{ enrolled_object.final_inspection_status }}. ", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "2", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-1", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "1"}, "fields": {"delta": "2", "time_unit": "MINUTES"}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "3", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "4"}, "fields": {"property_name": "inspection_update___sms", "value": {"staticValue": "Hi again, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers. The installation of your project is complete and your system is one step closer to powering your home! Next up is the Final Inspection, where your local building department ensures everything meets code, safety standards, and Photon Brothers\u2019 quality standards.\n\nWhat to Expect:\n\nWe\u2019ll schedule the inspection with the appropriate local authorities. Once it passes, we\u2019ll request Permission to Operate (PTO) from your utility. You do not need to be home for this inspection as long as we have access to the installed equipment.\n\nWe will be in touch once your Inspection has been scheduled.\n\nReply END to stop texts.", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "4", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-5", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "6"}, "fields": {"property_name": "inspection_update___email", "value": {"staticValue": "Hello, this is Olivia - Virtual Assistant with Photon Brothers.\n\nThe Installation of your project is complete and we will be moving to the Final Inspection and obtaining Permission to Operate. This is where we work with your local building department to ensure everything has been installed to meet local codes, safety requirements, and Photon Brothers' quality standards.\n\nWhat to Expect Next: \nWe\u2019ll schedule the Final Inspection with the appropriate local authorities. Once the inspection is passed, we\u2019ll move forward with obtaining Permission to Operate (PTO) from your utility company, which typically takes about two to four weeks. You do not need to be home for this inspection as long as we have access to the installed equipment.\n\nWe will be in touch once your Inspection has been scheduled.\n\nBest,\nPhoton Brothers", "type": "STATIC_VALUE"}}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "5", "method": "POST", "webhookUrl": "https://public.lindy.ai/api/v1/webhooks/lindy/d65c10cb-585b-490e-bac2-75be3b0d875b", "queryParams": [], "authSettings": {"secretName": "lindy_stage_change", "name": "Bearer", "location": "HEADER", "type": "AUTH_KEY"}, "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "7"}, "type": "WEBHOOK"}, {"actionId": "6", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-1", "connection": {"edgeType": "STANDARD", "nextActionId": "5"}, "fields": {"delta": "1", "time_unit": "MINUTES"}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}, {"actionId": "7", "actionTypeVersion": 0, "actionTypeId": "0-8", "fields": {"subject": "Bot Inspection Webhook Fired - {{ enrolled_object.dealname }}", "body": "<p>Bot Inspection Webhook Fired:<br>{{ enrolled_object.dealname }}<br><br><br>{{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153828494.firstname }} {{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153828494.lastname }}</p>\n<p>{{ fetched_objects.fetched_object_153828494.phone }}</p>", "owner_properties": ["project_manager"]}, "type": "SINGLE_CONNECTION"}], "enrollmentCriteria": {"shouldReEnroll": false, "listFilterBranch": {"filterBranches": [{"filterBranches": [], "filters": [{"property": "deal_closed_won", "operation": {"operator": "IS_EQUAL_TO", "includeObjectsWithNoValueSet": false, "value": true, "operationType": "BOOL"}, "filterType": "PROPERTY"}, {"property": "closedate", "operation": {"operator": "IS_KNOWN